<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>How to Get a Groq API Key</title>
<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 30px;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #111827;
    color: #f3f4f6;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: auto;
    background: #1f2937;
    border: 1px solid #374151;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  ol {
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  code {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding: 10px;
    background: #0f172a;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: #22c55e;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .note {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
  }

  .example-btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: white;
    background: #2563eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .example-btn:hover {
    background: #1d4ed8;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>How to Create a Groq API Key</h1>

  <ol>
    <li>
  Go to
  <a href="https://console.groq.com/" target="_blank" style="color:#60a5fa;">
    https://console.groq.com/
  </a>.
</li>
    <li>Sign in or create a Groq account.</li>
    <li>Open the <strong>API Keys</strong> page. (Top Right)</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Create API Key</strong>.</li>
    <li>Give your key a name. (can be anything)</li>
    <li>Copy the key</li>
    <li>Click the "Paste Here" button then Paste your Key</li>
  </ol>

  <code>
Example: gsk_vCcCLvQy1qyP1j16kZn0WGdyb3FYvxpvKZDV1UNONOhsb6NEq42Bi
  </code>

 

  <!-- Replace # with your desired URL -->

  <a href="https://google.com" target="_blank" class="example-btn">
     Paste Here
  </a>

</body>
</html>
